hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I went to shred her stack reviews Phase II of Obamacare will be building work prisons for those people that cannot afford to pay even the opt out amounts. Obamacare is nothing but a protection racket for the insurance corporations and enforced by the government/police. Pay up or else! It’s the law! It is now illegal to be alive without protection from an insurance company. Let that sink in for a moment. Every American citizen needs to be purchasing a product, for life, from a for-profit corporation or you will be considered a criminal. Jaw-dropping unbelievable.
